Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.01,0:02:33.01,LOGO2,,0,0,0,,招募聯繫QQ281118926
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.55,0:00:56.87,OP,,0,0,0,,look up at the sky\N仰望那片天空
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.97,0:00:59.63,OP,,0,0,0,,like a bird without wings\N如鸟儿失去翅膀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.67,0:01:01.87,OP,,0,0,0,,if you want to fly\N如果想要飞翔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.93,0:01:05.05,OP,,0,0,0,,feel your breath release yourself\N就去感觉你的呼吸 释放自己
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.05,0:01:06.85,OP,,0,0,0,,why do you sigh\N你为何叹息
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.05,0:01:09.63,OP,,0,0,0,,just count your blessings\N不如知足常乐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.63,0:01:11.71,OP,,0,0,0,,every time you try\N每一次做出尝试
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.93,0:01:18.79,OP,,0,0,0,,what some thing believes yourself\N都要相信自己
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.09,0:01:29.13,OP,,0,0,0,,my mission is gonna be a tough one\N我的任务将会艰巨无比
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.13,0:01:31.93,OP,,0,0,0,,i know it's not a game anymore\N也知道这不再是一场游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.93,0:01:34.83,OP,,0,0,0,,i swear that i'll never fail again\N我发誓将不再失败
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.83,0:01:37.93,OP,,0,0,0,,cause i don't wanna regret anymore \N因为不想让自己再后悔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.93,0:01:40.67,OP,,0,0,0,,can you hera i'm calling you\N是否听到我在呼唤你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.79,0:01:43.39,OP,,0,0,0,,i just wanna feel you\N我只是想要触碰到你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.55,0:01:45.99,OP,,0,0,0,,don't forget to remember \N别忘了要记住
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.99,0:01:49.03,OP,,0,0,0,,so please remember\N所以请记住
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.19,0:01:51.93,OP,,0,0,0,,i hear you air calling me\N我听到你气息的呼唤
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.05,0:01:54.73,OP,,0,0,0,,i want you to feel me\N我想让你来触碰我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.89,0:01:57.35,OP,,0,0,0,,you know i want to surrender \N你知道我想要放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.35,0:02:00.19,OP,,0,0,0,,never surrender \N决不放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.19,0:02:03.03,OP,,0,0,0,,my mission i've got to execute\N我的任务我必须完成
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.03,0:02:05.83,OP,,0,0,0,,i know it'w not a game anymore\N我知道这已不再是游戏
